33:26.966 --> 33:32.973
Don't try to return strength to your own soul without doing what David did and don't do it in isolation.

33:34.374 --> 33:38.499
This is why it's important to be together regularly with other believers.

33:40.001 --> 33:40.521
Very important.

33:40.882 --> 33:42.103
God designed it like that.

33:43.945 --> 33:44.786
There is no other way.

33:45.727 --> 33:48.050
God's given you leaders and pastors

33:48.578 --> 33:51.441
Other people like mentors and friends to help you.

33:52.022 --> 33:53.984
Does your soul need strength to return?

33:54.084 --> 33:54.405
Anybody?

33:55.346 --> 33:56.567
Raise your hand right now.

33:56.907 --> 33:58.069
You need strength in your soul.

33:58.109 --> 33:58.369
You do?

33:58.449 --> 33:59.330
Yes, yes.

33:59.350 --> 33:59.791
Anybody else?

34:00.492 --> 34:01.052
Anybody over here?

34:01.993 --> 34:02.794
Strength in your soul.

34:02.834 --> 34:03.635
You need it to come back.

34:03.655 --> 34:03.855
Yes.

34:04.576 --> 34:04.816
Yes.

34:05.818 --> 34:08.421
Jesus, I thank you, Lord, that you're the one.

34:08.721 --> 34:10.223
You put us on paths of righteousness.

34:10.243 --> 34:11.084
You're a perfect shepherd.

34:11.344 --> 34:14.207
You are so skilled at shepherding our lives.

34:15.188 --> 34:16.690
We looked at that last Lord's day.

34:17.762 --> 34:22.669
And so God, we're going to comprehensively understand and realize that you're always active.

34:23.250 --> 34:25.093
You're always active in our life, even now.

34:25.614 --> 34:27.877
Bring this revelation to the people that raise their hands.

34:29.339 --> 34:30.701
And oh God, we pray that you would help.

34:32.744 --> 34:38.813
Help us, Lord, to be constant in following the directions that you have given us, the paths that have been put before us.

34:42.899 --> 34:45.042
I pray that you would overwhelm these dear people that

34:45.250 --> 34:49.356
Need strength in their soul, overwhelm them with your love and grace and your mercy right now.

34:50.497 --> 34:51.559
Holy spirit right now.

34:54.903 --> 35:07.440
God, I pray as we sing this last song that even during that song, every word, Holy spirit that you would do this for those people that raised their hands, strengthen their soul alone.

35:07.460 --> 35:08.381
We thank you, Jesus.

35:08.521 --> 35:09.182
Can we all stand?

35:09.783 --> 35:10.764
We thank you, Jesus.

35:11.646 --> 35:12.467
This is who you are.

35:13.989 --> 35:14.930
This is who you are.

35:17.218 --> 35:17.979
Can I see those hands?

35:18.060 --> 35:20.103
Again, raise those hands who raised them in just a second.

35:20.163 --> 35:21.446
I'm not going to ask you to come out or anything.

35:22.147 --> 35:23.650
God's touching your life right now.

35:23.690 --> 35:25.934
He's doing it supernaturally.

35:26.916 --> 35:28.018
He's doing it through His Word.

35:28.539 --> 35:32.927
He's doing it here in the atmosphere of His presence in this room.

35:35.011 --> 35:36.754
Let's worship Him with one more song.

35:48.930 --> 35:52.817
Thanks for listening to the Crossway Christian Church's Middleford campus sermon podcast.

35:53.138 --> 36:00.371
If you like to plug into the life of our community or have any questions that we might be able to answer, visit our website at crosswaycc.org to connect with us.

36:00.832 --> 36:02.115
Until next time, we can be with you.

36:02.395 --> 36:04.018
May the Lord bless you and keep you.

